2. -----------------------------------------------------
To get hardened executable change:

From
CFLAGS = -Wall -g -O2
to
CFLAGS = -Wall -g -O2       -fPIE  -fstack-protector

From
LDFLAGS = 
to
LDFLAGS = -pie -Wl,-z,now,-z,relro

